title: All Permutations of a String
description: A permutation of a string is a rearrangement of its characters. In this problem, you are given a string `S`. Your task is to generate and print all possible permutations of the characters in `S`. The output must be sorted alphabetically (lexicographically).
output_format: Output all distinct permutations of the string `S`, each on a new line. Ensure the output is sorted lexicographically.

ABC
ACB
BAC
BCA
CAB
CBA
